## Spring Cloud Netflix

Spring Cloud Netflix provides Netflix OSS integrations for Spring Boot apps through
autoconfiguration and binding to the Spring Environment and other Spring programming 
model idioms. With a few simple annotations you can quickly enable and configure the 
common patterns inside your application and build large distributed systems with 
battle-tested Netflix components.
The patterns provided include Service Discovery (Eureka),
Circuit Breaker (Hystrix), Intelligent Routing (Zuul) and Client Side Load Balancing (Ribbon)..

## ELK(Elasticsearch-Logstash-Kibana)

The ELK stack is composed of:

    Elasticsearch for indexing the data (logs and metrics)
    Logstash to manage and process the logs received from the applications
    Kibana to visualize the logs with a nice interface

